text:
Every time I find a place that's great, I feel bad because then I know I will:
1) Spend more money;
2) Very possibly, gain unnecessary amount of weight;
3) Probably eat something I am intolerant to and give me some sort of reaction;
4) ALL WILL BE WELL WORTH!

Cafe Breizh is one of those places. The ambience is open, clean and uncluttered, without feeling sterile. The place is a gem! I could easily eat 5 croissants by myself. Yikes!
